{"tid":2026312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"527出去嘅同我入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-05-21T01:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T02:00:02.000Z","uid":250291,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f0be459d7c4550296c7182b2398c04c45850f87","tid":2026312,"uid":250291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0afNthb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0afNthb.jpg&h=e48ba92e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n老實講<br />\n如果我地527嗰日仲諗住用平時嘅方法打嘅話<br />\n結局相信都無咩懸念<br />\n班狗落重兵 成朝都聚唔到人 馬路都佔唔到條 最後阻唔到開會...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">雖然係咁 我都會照出去的<br />\n不過我更加希望每人入到嚟 擺低一個新嘅idea<br />\n睇下有咩第二D可行嘅方法 戰略<br />\n可以避免到527成為一次大濫捕嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩即管講 我試下盡覆</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 呀係 有D人將612心態放落去527到<br />\n咩武力差距嘅問題已經不在話下<br />\n最重要嘅係 <span style=\"color: red;\">612之所以贏係因為柒婆當初主動暫緩</span><br />\n你阻到527審蟈歌法 你估柒婆仲會暫緩咩 佢最多下個星期三咪又再嚟過<br />\n大家要有心理準備。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befbdc6a6889ba769961b42278e138564027c091","tid":2026312,"uid":250291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:06:44.000Z","msg":"自推八連<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光"},{"pid":"c280893a3dcd27cfe3f3b9985f5c5568d5501764","tid":2026312,"uid":250291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:06:54.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"b0bba2d9ea233136cf65f9595c716c9f0e733a58","tid":2026312,"uid":250291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:07:04.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"cb06de50831998ccae28094b4b6725244efb859e","tid":2026312,"uid":250291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:07:14.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"7609b6b6abb272354266ad5cd73bd0dd78ba068a","tid":2026312,"uid":25